! 和频

$$
\omega_3=\omega_1+\omega_2
$$

假设：泵浦光$$\omega_2$$足够大，传播过程中振幅几乎不变；满足相位匹配条件

耦合波方程
$$
\begin{aligned}
\frac{\partial A_1(z)}{\partial z}&=\imath g_{SF}A_3(z)\\
\frac{\partial A_3(z)}{\partial z}&=\imath g_{SF}A_1(z)
\end{aligned}
$$
其中，$$A_i(z)=\sqrt{\frac{n_i}{\omega_i}}E_i(z),g_{SF}=\frac{4\chi^{(2)}}{c}\sqrt{\frac{\omega_1\omega_3}{n_1n_3}}E_2(0)$$(和频增益系数)

解得
$$
\begin{aligned}
A_3(z)&=\imath A_1(0)\sin(g_{SF}z)\\
A_1(z)&=\imath A_1(0)\cos(g_{SF}z)
\end{aligned}
$$

和频转换效率
$$
\eta=\frac{I_3(L)}{I_1(0)}=\frac{\omega_3}{\omega_1}\sin^2(g_{SF}L)
$$
